    "body" : "<p>In case you need to inject an empty (0 length) <code>&quot;&quot;</code> string as the <code>@Value</code> default - use SPEL (spring expression language) as follows:</p>\n<pre><code>@Value(&quot;${index.suffix:#{''}}&quot;) \nprivate String indexSuffix;\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>#{''}</code> just gets you an empty string as injected <code>@Value</code>'s default.</p>\n"
  } ],
